Dialogue: 5,0:00:03.89,0:00:05.26,Default,,0,0,20,,I'll be damned...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:05.26,0:00:08.37,Default,,0,0,20,,This is where we stored all the sacred relics recovered from the seafloor
Dialogue: 5,0:00:08.37,0:00:11.24,Default,,0,0,20,,that are suspected to be weapons.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:11.63,0:00:14.25,Default,,0,0,20,,Wh-What a heap of treasure!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:14.25,0:00:17.25,Default,,0,0,20,,Your sacred duty is to repair these.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:17.56,0:00:19.45,Default,,0,0,20,,Easier said than done!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:19.45,0:00:21.86,Default,,0,0,20,,I don't even know where to sta—
Dialogue: 5,0:00:22.91,0:00:23.67,Default,,0,0,20,,What's this?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:26.51,0:00:27.84,Default,,0,0,20,,This lets me look inside them?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:28.39,0:00:30.44,Default,,0,0,20,,Damn, that's awesome!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:30.44,0:00:34.43,Default,,0,0,20,,Any item that does not add to\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}our armament is yours to keep.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:34.43,0:00:35.01,Default,,0,0,20,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:36.81,0:00:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:37.97,0:00:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hold you to that!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:40.81,0:00:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:51.87,0:00:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:52.89,0:00:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What a shallow man.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:54.61,0:00:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:57.24,0:00:59.70,Default,,0,0,20,,I was remarking on how easily bought you are.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:00.19,0:01:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:01.56,0:01:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem so satisfied with\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}what you've been given.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:04.30,0:01:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I took you for a more\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}willful man than that.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:07.96,0:01:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's your point?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:10.99,0:01:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The flying Yunboro...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:13.17,0:01:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the metalhead?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:15.00,0:01:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Provided we can make use of it,\NI might be willing to aid you.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:18.90,0:01:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't see your point.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:20.68,0:01:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As a matter of fact, I am quite disgusted\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}with the ways of this fleet.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:26.23,0:01:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:28.60,0:01:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to being a pirate.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:31.43,0:01:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,After I sink this fleet, that is.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:47.74,0:01:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:52.05,0:01:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you refrain from attacking Gargantia?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:56.13,0:01:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:57.43,0:01:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:58.77,0:02:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to help them, then hasten our missionary work.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:06.05,0:02:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let us turn them into useful human resources
Dialogue: 5,0:02:08.74,0:02:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,for the sake of mankind's prosperity!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:10.97,0:02:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:13.39,0:02:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo, it is our duty to bring\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}a new order to this planet.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:17.97,0:02:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's no different from\N{\alpha&HFF&}...{\r}the Galactic Alliance...
Dialogue: 5,0:02:20.95,0:02:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we be unable to\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}reunite with the fleet,
Dialogue: 5,0:02:23.33,0:02:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we will transform this planet, Earth,\Ninto our own utopia—a second Avalon.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:29.21,0:02:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Our legitimacy remains unchanged.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:31.57,0:02:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Falter not.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.20,0:02:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.01,0:02:41.97,epTitle,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\pos(640,440)}Moment of Decision
Dialogue: 5,0:02:54.21,0:02:56.15,Default,,0,0,10,,This baby's pretty awesome too!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:56.15,0:02:58.39,Default,,0,0,10,,Lord Pinion, you have a visitor.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:58.39,0:02:59.90,Default,,0,0,10,,Ah, let 'em through.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.94,0:03:03.71,Default,,0,0,10,,{\i1}Lord{\i0} Pinion?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:03.71,0:03:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Like some nobleman!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:05.49,0:03:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just you?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:07.42,0:03:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can inspect all the goods you like?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:09.66,0:03:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When did you become such a big shot?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:12.46,0:03:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I never asked for this.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:14.33,0:03:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:23.35,0:03:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Avalon.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:25.35,0:03:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Utopia.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:31.77,0:03:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,...we will transform this planet, Earth,\Ninto our own utopia—a second Avalon!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:37.32,0:03:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Falter not.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.43,0:03:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Grace?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.13,0:03:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:53.40,0:03:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.29,0:03:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Grace is on Gargantia.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:58.10,0:03:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,With Amy.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.97,0:04:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.23,0:04:10.28,Default,,0,0,90,,He's here!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:10.28,0:04:11.25,Default,,0,0,90,,Pinion!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:12.04,0:04:13.65,Default,,0,0,90,,Keep it short.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:13.65,0:04:16.61,Default,,0,0,90,,What's with the members of this fleet?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:17.07,0:04:17.77,Default,,0,0,90,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:18.26,0:04:20.65,Default,,0,0,90,,They might as well be ghosts!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:20.65,0:04:23.35,Default,,0,0,90,,It's like they're possessed.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:23.35,0:04:24.74,Default,,0,0,90,,It's weird!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:25.51,0:04:26.49,Default,,0,0,90,,I guess.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:27.14,0:04:31.87,Default,,0,0,90,,If this goes on, the people on my ships\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}are bound to end up the same way.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:32.52,0:04:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\move(640,630,640,685,1250,1500)}And then, what would have been the point of leaving Gargantia?!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:36.39,0:04:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to let that happen?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:41.69,0:04:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's planning a revolt.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.92,0:04:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:44.92,0:04:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.67,0:04:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the Red Lobster who greeted me.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:49.13,0:04:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The great pirate Rackage?{ep3}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.78,0:04:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then, if you pair up with the Lobster and—
Dialogue: 5,0:04:53.95,0:04:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants the metalhead, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.84,0:04:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't see Ledo agreeing to that one.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:00.25,0:05:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:01.59,0:05:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we gonna have to\Nlive like this forever?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:21.67,0:05:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}Spread it out and collect the water!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:27.95,0:05:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're soaked.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.66,0:05:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna catch a cold like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.05,0:05:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:50.90,0:05:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.02,0:05:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.82,0:05:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Chamber, what's going on?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.77,0:06:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the natural phenomenon\Nwe observed earlier called "rain."
Dialogue: 5,0:06:03.72,0:06:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not detect anything\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}out of the ordinary.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:19.87,0:06:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What... is that?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:26.65,0:06:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.94,0:06:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The gift bestowed by the great God\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}in the skies is a wonderful blessing.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:48.10,0:06:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Their journey to stand by\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}God's side begins here.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:51.26,0:06:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,As a manifestation of our fervent gratitude,\Nthey shall die for the sake of those who live!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.10,0:06:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.26,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:00.33,0:07:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,They receive this eternal glory\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}for the salvation of mankind.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:21.74,0:07:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,People...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:22.75,0:07:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are people, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:27.46,0:07:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here to witness this.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They're insane.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:39.26,0:07:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, they are.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:41.95,0:07:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And this insane fleet's next target is...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.63,0:07:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Gargantia.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:47.90,0:07:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:54.76,0:07:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess this ain't gonna\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}work out after all.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.31,0:08:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I came here to protect them\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r\i1}all from the Hideauze.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:05.36,0:08:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amy.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.75,0:08:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bevel.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.75,0:08:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to protect all those people!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:11.17,0:08:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:53.15,0:08:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Orders received from Colonel Kugel:
Dialogue: 5,0:08:55.21,0:08:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,"Second Lieutenant Ledo is\Nto prepare for combat."
Dialogue: 5,0:08:58.09,0:08:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,"To me, soldier."
Dialogue: 5,0:09:03.53,0:09:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I await your decision.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,My decision, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:11.10,0:09:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I decide, and you execute.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.88,0:09:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it's always been.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:18.84,0:09:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, I've never made a\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}single real decision in my life.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:27.67,0:09:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The meaning of your words is unclear.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.01,0:09:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Colonel's orders—
Dialogue: 5,0:09:31.02,0:09:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Chamber!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:31.94,0:09:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How is your combat potential\Ncompared to Striker's?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:35.48,0:09:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Cannot be determined\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}due to lack of data.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.07,0:09:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The intent of your query is unclear.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:43.33,0:09:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you fight Striker?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:47.80,0:09:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.48,0:09:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Striker X3752 is currently operating\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}without orders from the Galactic Alliance.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:56.76,0:09:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It can be considered a\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}possible combat opponent.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.71,0:10:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:00.89,0:10:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:01.95,0:10:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,can I fight the colonel?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:07.81,0:10:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Chamber!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:09.41,0:10:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Answering that is beyond my\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}capabilities as a pilot support system.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:15.24,0:10:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Decisions regarding combat objectives\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}are left to you under all circumstances.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.83,0:10:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:48.86,0:10:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Radio transmissions would be intercepted.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.29,0:10:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We must warn them directly.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.67,0:10:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We're out of time!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:55.02,0:10:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't leave such an\N{\alpha&HFF&}...{\r}important mission to me...
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.16,0:11:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one here who can\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}fly all the way to Gargantia.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:02.38,0:11:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! Save them all!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.05,0:11:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You owe me one, okay?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:24.73,0:11:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chamber. Stand by for combat.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:27.70,0:11:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:05.60,0:12:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Gargantia...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:29.44,0:12:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Melty!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:32.19,0:12:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It really {\i1}was{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.74,0:12:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy... Amy!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:37.06,0:12:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna attack Gargantia...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.60,0:12:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Melty?!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:42.51,0:12:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What a crazy girl.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:44.00,0:12:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,She flew all the way here\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}by herself on a surfkite.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:51.35,0:12:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Melty!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:52.20,0:12:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Saya... Amy...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:59.20,0:13:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,To protect Gargantia,
Dialogue: 5,0:13:01.25,0:13:05.93,Default,,0,0,90,,our only option is to follow Melty's instruction:\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}change our course and attempt to flee.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:06.34,0:13:09.34,Default,,0,0,90,,As commodore, I have to agree—
Dialogue: 5,0:13:09.82,0:13:10.80,Default,,0,0,90,,Wait!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:11.12,0:13:12.11,Default,,0,0,90,,Amy?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:14.88,0:13:20.94,Default,,0,0,90,,Melty told me that Ledo wants to\Ntake them on while we escape!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:21.74,0:13:22.69,Default,,0,0,90,,What?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:23.06,0:13:25.20,Default,,0,0,90,,He's gonna fight! By himself!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:25.20,0:13:26.61,Default,,0,0,90,,In our place!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.35,0:13:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll even go against his own comrade, just to protect Gargantia!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.62,0:13:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And you still want to run away?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:34.87,0:13:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about that?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.99,0:13:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:43.99,0:13:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He made his choice.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:47.30,0:13:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We must make ours too.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:50.78,0:13:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Ordum...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:53.28,0:13:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridget.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:54.66,0:13:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it is high time we used the key.{GO TO THE BASEMENT EREN}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:00.30,0:14:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The Stairway to Heaven?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:04.58,0:14:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:06.08,0:14:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Such is my advice to the Commodore\Nas the wise man of this fleet.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:13.30,0:14:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.49,0:14:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Amy.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.73,0:14:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to help too.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:23.23,0:14:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hear my almighty will.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:25.49,0:14:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,To demonstrate God's\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}boundless might to the world,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:29.14,0:14:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I hereby announce the beginning\Nof a new crusade!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:33.02,0:14:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall be victorious
Dialogue: 5,0:14:35.62,0:14:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and bring absolute order to this planet.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:39.79,0:14:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall build a glorious and prosperous\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}utopia on this planet.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.78,0:14:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Obey me. Nothing more is required.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.11,0:14:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I will lead you to eternal well-being.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:12.18,0:15:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:18.19,0:15:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Lieutenant Ledo,\Nexplain your absurd behavior.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:21.83,0:15:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one being absurd!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:24.08,0:15:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Such words hardly befit\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}a soldier of the Alliance.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.27,0:15:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Earth, not the Galactic Alliance!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.07,0:15:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, it is a planet\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}inhabited by mankind.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:32.34,0:15:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It is our duty to enlighten them.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:35.49,0:15:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Duty?!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:36.97,0:15:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.38,0:15:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The people of this planet have\Nbuilt their own world here!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.39,0:15:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing can justify destroying that!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:44.25,0:15:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Our legitimacy remains unchanged.{line 44}
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.02,0:15:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Falter not.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:04.19,0:16:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your distance!\NThis is a battle of the gods!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.26,0:16:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it so powerful?!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:42.95,0:16:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I hypothesize that it is not\Nlimited to its own generator
Dialogue: 5,0:16:44.79,0:16:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but has been able to draw power\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}from an external energy source.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:47.35,0:16:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So he was charging up?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:54.14,0:16:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:55.60,0:17:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It is our duty to bring a\Nnew order to this planet.{l.40}
Dialogue: 5,0:17:07.31,0:17:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinion?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:08.88,0:17:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinon, withdraw!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:10.53,0:17:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my battle!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.96,0:17:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.62,0:17:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You space boys sure get on my nerves,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:15.18,0:17:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but that's nothin' compared\Nto those religious nutjobs!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:19.01,0:17:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Next shot charged and ready!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.47,0:17:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill them!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:30.66,0:17:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:36.10,0:17:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,All civilians not participating in the attack,\Ntake shelter in the cargo hangars!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:41.26,0:17:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare the rescue pods!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:43.73,0:17:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That vessel is the fleet's main ship!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:46.29,0:17:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Seize control of it at all costs!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:49.75,0:17:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Quell the revolt!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:51.21,0:17:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All who oppose us are enemies!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:16.82,0:18:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Her?!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:22.48,0:18:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Please pardon my uncomely entrance.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:46.89,0:18:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually acting like a man for once?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:49.60,0:18:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,My opinion of you has improved.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:50.89,0:18:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:52.00,0:18:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Get rid of those guys,\Nand get over here!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:53.81,0:18:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mind if I do.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:16.86,0:19:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Unable to establish tactical dominance.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.51,0:19:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A temporary retreat is suggested.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:22.13,0:19:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Focus fire on the enemy cockpit.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:25.05,0:19:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to kill the colonel!
Dialogue: 5,0:19:29.93,0:19:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Warning: enemy unit on collision course.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:37.07,0:19:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Both the strong and the weak\N{\alpha&HFF&}.{\r}support each other with reason.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:41.66,0:19:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That is what it means to be human.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:44.36,0:19:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:45.87,0:19:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ledo!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:00.51,0:20:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:03.80,0:20:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:11.05,0:20:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinion?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:11.81,0:20:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:19.11,0:20:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Generator at maximum output!
Dialogue: 5,0:20:44.61,0:20:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Ledo. Won't you help\Nme change this planet?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:00.53,0:21:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Going in.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:02.27,0:21:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Send emergency release signal.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:05.99,0:21:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Having you around will help a lot.{ep11}
Dialogue: 5,0:21:25.31,0:21:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:26.29,0:21:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you follow me... once more...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:37.36,0:21:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Colonel...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:42.40,0:21:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Rebooting posture control system.
Dialogue: 5,0:22:03.20,0:22:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Lieutenant Ledo,\Nyour resistance is futile.
